@Node "INT" "Introduction"

@{b}@{u}Introduction@{uu}@{ub}

Use ScreenToIFF to save open screens (public or private) as IFF-ILBM pictures.
Unfortunately, it is not (yet) able to save graphics card screens.


@Endnode
@Node "SYR" "System requirements"

@{b}@{u}System requirements@{uu}@{ub}

ScreenToIFF requires Kickstart 2.04+ and the following libraries in the LIBS:
directory:

   - diskfont.library
   - asl.library


@Endnode
@Node "INS" "Installation"

@{b}@{u}Installation@{uu}@{ub}

To install ScreenToIFF, simply drag its icon to any drawer of your choice.


@Endnode
